refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arrayposix_getpwnam stringusername
Возвращает array с информацией о переданном пользователе.

&reftitle.examples;
Пример использования posix_getpwnam
<?php
$userinfo = posix_getpwnam("tom");
print_r($userinfo); ?>
&example.outputs.similar;
Array ( [name] => tom [passwd] => x [uid] => 10000 [gid] => 42 [gecos] => "tom,,," [dir] => "/home/tom" [shell] => "/bin/bash" )
